oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Grover Cleveland Adkins in his office at the Montgomery County Courthouse, ca. 1936-1937
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Grover Cleveland Adkins (center) and two unidentified individuals in his office at the Montgomery County Courthouse. Grover Cleveland served as the County Court Register from 1934-1954.
